Package controller

Class PhotoDisplayController

java.lang.Object
controller.PhotoDisplayController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ErrorMessage, Logout
public class PhotoDisplayController extends Object implements ErrorMessage, Logout
This controller controls the PhotoList.fxml and PhotoSearch.fxml files. This controller implements the ErrorMessage and Logout interfaces.
